{"tid":2290434,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警長劉志豪自言認為被告「比較大隻」，旁聽席即傳來：「咁都大隻？」","createTime":"2020-11-18T04:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T03:46:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":296,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"7fced0b066a2607e8b73f76c232570873584b523","tid":2290434,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:03:16.000Z","msg":"警長劉志豪自言認為被告「比較大隻」，旁聽席即傳來：「咁都大隻？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201118/2HOKCA7YKRHEHKNAR746I7I7CM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201118%2F2HOKCA7YKRHEHKNAR746I7I7CM%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1T2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=92375de5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201118%2F2HOKCA7YKRHEHKNAR746I7I7CM%2F&h=87e4634c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201118/2HOKCA7YKRHEHKNAR746I7I7CM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警指瘦削被告「大隻凶暴」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rsUrfZoFjfSsgMrFHBp-q69XwOM=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VWHSNUQZ6NEGXGHWOG7W4TYXFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrsUrfZoFjfSsgMrFHBp-q69XwOM%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVWHSNUQZ6NEGXGHWOG7W4TYXFU.jpg&h=d76f4e60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【一打三襲警案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】理大畢業生被指去年7月14日在新城市廣場被捕後，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。，當日帶領下屬包括許智星、焦國榮、梁健聰及女警到葵涌警署，協助處理被捕人士錄取背景口供的文書工作，其間發生被告襲警事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聞旁聽席譁然即改口<br />\n<br />\n辯方質疑劉動員四人為被告錄取背景口供原因。<span class=\"orange\">劉自言認為被告「比較大隻」，旁聽席即傳來：「咁都大隻？」</span>劉及後改口稱：「。。。。。。。。。」。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n女警謝熙鈫則供稱，當日只有一次隨同袍押解一名被捕人士到會面室，但途中警長指示她回羈留室繼續看守工作。她對被告沒有印象，並否認曾爆粗罵他或襲擊他。<br />\n<br />\n被告被裁定表證成立後自辯，他說被帶至會面室時，發現裏面沒有閉路電視設備，遂不肯入內，同時要求見值日官但遭拒。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n被告友人陳雨嫣作供指稱，去年7月14日晚上與被告一同被捕後，遭帶到警署臨時羈留區，他看到一名女警向被告指罵：「睥乜X嘢？坐直啲啦！我認得你，連登仔吖嘛！」隨後被告被帶走。案件下月31日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：STCC2841/19"},{"pid":"7d18a2baebbb48042235b9b165f0a4382c59a899","tid":2290434,"uid":266010,"like":322,"dislike":2,"score":320,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就嚟厭食症都好撚大隻"},{"pid":"ca7696ebac7cb57d529e210f4be582aacf11e833","tid":2290434,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:04:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acac435a37763950b8a45a0b01d4b018918f052d","tid":2290434,"uid":334957,"like":280,"dislike":1,"score":279,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"我認得你，連登仔吖嘛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188c25fe79c749eaeef82b0ba75e00dd0cea6313","tid":2290434,"uid":334957,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"quote":{"pid":"acac435a37763950b8a45a0b01d4b018918f052d","tid":2290434,"uid":334957,"like":280,"dislike":1,"score":279,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"我認得你，連登仔吖嘛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":