sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c175c82c0b8a479e31abd7c2b6e88fc7b8e041","tid":2290434,"uid":101756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9db3197626f96dd1e7fe826c9649c07946238673","tid":2290434,"uid":187489,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"你上左連登幾多年 連highlight都唔識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重點明明喺呢段入面！<br />\n<br />\n當日帶領下屬包括許智星、焦國榮、梁健聰及女警到葵涌警署，協助處理被捕人士錄取背景口供的文書工作，其間發生被告襲警事件。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:54:44.000Z","msg":"強姦女手足果間曱甴屋"},{"pid":"bbf593f6849950807e94e75ebce47578251749ff","tid":2290434,"uid":195248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"acac435a37763950b8a45a0b01d4b018918f052d","tid":2290434,"uid":334957,"like":280,"dislike":1,"score":279,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"我認得你，連登仔吖嘛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:55:12.000Z","msg":"仆街 咁都比佢認到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d886f2260c2c0fcad66e66582929507d7310ed","tid":2290434,"uid":40779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:55:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">咁都大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"a08dfabfbdb7dd6b5ba8acbd462a30d2973c2172","tid":2290434,"uid":267702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fced0b066a2607e8b73f76c232570873584b523","tid":2290434,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:03:16.000Z","msg":"警長劉志豪自言認為被告「比較大隻」，旁聽席即傳來：「咁都大隻？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201118/2HOKCA7YKRHEHKNAR746I7I7CM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201118%2F2HOKCA7YKRHEHKNAR746I7I7CM%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1T2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=92375de5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201118%2F2HOKCA7YKRHEHKNAR746I7I7CM%2F&h=87e4634c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201118/2HOKCA7YKRHEHKNAR746I7I7CM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警指瘦削被告「大隻凶暴」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rsUrfZoFjfSsgMrFHBp-q69XwOM=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VWHSNUQZ6NEGXGHWOG7W4TYXFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrsUrfZoFjfSsgMrFHBp-q69XwOM%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVWHSNUQZ6NEGXGHWOG7W4TYXFU.jpg&h=d76f4e60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【一打三襲警案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】理大畢業生被指去年7月14日在新城市廣場被捕後，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。，當日帶領下屬包括許智星、焦國榮、梁健聰及女警到葵涌警署，協助處理被捕人士錄取背景口供的文書工作，其間發生被告襲警事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聞旁聽席譁然即改口<br />\n<br />\n辯方質疑劉動員四人為被告錄取背景口供原因。<span class=\"orange\">劉自言認為被告「比較大隻」，旁聽席即傳來：「咁都大隻？」</span>劉及後改口稱：「。。。。。。。。。」。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n女警謝熙鈫則供稱，當日只有一次隨同袍押解一名被捕人士到會面室，但途中警長指示她回羈留室繼續看守工作。她對被告沒有印象，並否認曾爆粗罵他或襲擊他。<br />\n<br />\n被告被裁定表證成立後自辯，他說被帶至會面室時，發現裏面沒有閉路電視設備，遂不肯入內，同時要求見值日官但遭拒。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n被告友人陳雨嫣作供指稱，去年7月14日晚上與被告一同被捕後，遭帶到警署臨時羈留區，他看到一名女警向被告指罵：「睥乜X嘢？坐直啲啦！我認得你，連登仔吖嘛！」隨後被告被帶走。案件下月31日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：STCC2841/19"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:55:52.000Z","msg":"林鄭身材好豐滿，好撚正。"},{"pid":"d991d43da997181792a389cc3a809e320d6ad29e","tid":2290434,"uid":149607,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"acac435a37763950b8a45a0b01d4b018918f052d","tid":2290434,"uid":334957,"like":280,"dislike":1,"score":279,"citedBy":6,"reply